rComments: Sympathetic and really tried to inspire students. Helpful at office hours in walking through problem sets and all-around friendly. Many problem sets (8), although they were not long. Be prepared for tricky MC q's on midterm and final. Many opportunities for bonus marks on problem sets and presentation. Favorite course and best mark so far.
She's very friendly and encouraging. A great way to ease into the university process. AST222 will be a cold bucket of water though, so watch out.

Prof Wu is very approachable and really goes "above and beyond" for those who seek help from her. Her teaching style was a bit different from what I'm used to, and the assignments and tests were quite challenging, but if you put the effort in, she really teaches you to understand the concepts, not merely plug numbers into the equations.
